==English==
===Verb===
'''[[let]] [[sleeping]] [[dogs]] [[lie]]'''
#{{idiom}} To leave things as they are; especially, to avoid [[restarting]] or [[rekindling]] an old [[argument]]; to leave [[disagreements]] in the past.
#:''Eventually, they decided it would be best to '''let sleeping dogs lie''' and not discuss the matter any further.

====Translation====
German: [[Schlafende Hunde weckt man nicht]]